<p>I am trying to open a modal in cfc through a button in cfm. here is what I have so far. What do I need to change?</p>  <pre><code>&lt;button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="openModal" data-a="openmodal"&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;  $(document).on('click', '#openModal', function(){                      var a= $(this).data('a');                           $.ajax({                           url:'components/index.cfc?method=doShowModal&amp;a=' + a,                            success:function(){                              $("#myModal").modal('show');                               }                     });         });  &lt;cffunction name="doShowModal" access="remote"&gt;     &lt;cfargument name="a" required="true" /&gt;           &lt;cfsavecontent variable="modal"&gt;             modal will be here         &lt;/cfsavecontent&gt;     &lt;cfreturn modal /&gt; &lt;/cffunction&gt; </code></pre>